	LONDON (AP) -- Share prices fell Monday on the London Stock  
Exchange. 
</P>
<P>
	The Financial Times-Stock Exchange 100-share index was down 10.4  
points, or 0.2 percent, at 6,152.80. 
</P>
<P>
