<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Stock prices have opened narrowly mixed. The Dow  
Jones industrial average is down 14 points in today's early 
trading. Advancers and decliners are evenly split on the New York 
Stock Exchange. The Nasdaq Composite Index is up six points and the 
